summary: Hi can you please do a Marvel matchup for me? I'm a girl, my height is around 4'11 (I'm short I know) and I can be a little bit...
question: Hi can you please do a Marvel matchup for me? I'm a girl, my height is around 4'11 (I'm short I know) and I can be a little bit annoying at times. I'm shy with new people but once I get to know them, I become really chatty and chirpy. Oversensitive and love protection from others, hate when people rely on me but also hate being instructed by others. I can be clingy as hell once I'm attached to someone. Thanks.
answer:
I match you with Loki! 

Loki adores you. He loves your shortness and he can definitely top you at being annoying and he loves how you can switch from quiet to extra chatty, it doesn’t bother him one bit. And he’s hella protective over you, and he knows how you feel about being instructed to do things, so he’ll let you do your own thing, unless of course things are getting out of hand ;) Loves your clinginess since it makes him feel appreciated.

title: Hold My Hand
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2Js70G5

by shenala

Prompt: “Your hand is so sweaty” “Deal with it, we’re holding hands.”

When he woke up that morning, the air felt like change. Sure, it looked like the start of any other day with Steve wrapped around him and the sheets tangled by their feet, and it sounded like the many mornings before with the muffled New York noise rising up to their window (they had specifically requested “a little less soundproofing, please Tony” to stop it being too quiet) and the quiet hiss of the coffee machine starting up in the kitchen.
